{
  "texts": [
    "LSTM and Bi-LSTM with Root Mean Square Propagation (RMSprop) optimizer provided the best accuracy among the other deep learning models.Al-Yahya et al. [45] performed another comparison study between the use of the NN model and the transformer-based language model for detecting Arabic fake news.",
    "The datasets used in this study included ArCOV19-Rumors, AraNews [84], Arabic News Stance (ANS) corpus [85], and COVID-19-Fakes [74].",
    "The study used a linear model at word and character levels with Glove, Word2Vec, FastText, and document level.",
    "For the classification tasks, deep learning models CNN, GRU, and RNN were used.",
    "Moreover, QARiB, AraBERT, ArELectra, ARBERT, and MARBERT were used from the transformer-based models."
  ]
}